item.title: About Page
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: 1. Atmosphere is simply divine. Introducing the most beautiful theme ever created for the Genesis Framework. With an emphasis on incredible typography and responsive design, this HTML5 theme will leave your audience nothing short of speechless. 2. Your typography matters. Typography is, quite simply, the art and technique of arranging type. It's central to the work and skills of a designer and is about much more than making the words legible. Your choice of typeface and how you make it work heavily impacts the experience of your site visitor. 3. Responsive websites rock. Mobile responsive design is all about automatically delivering your audience the content they want, within the context that they’re viewing it. It’s revolutionary for online publishers, because it eliminates the need for multiple versions of your site, or app development.
